<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ب ص:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَبْصُ)</span> التَّنَاوُلُ بِأَطْرَافِ الْأَصَابِعِ.<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهُ قَرَأَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> <span class="c2">«فَقَبَصْتُ قَبْصَةً مِنْ أَثَرِ الرَّسُولِ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>